---
import Container from "./container.astro";
import Sectionhead from "./sectionhead.astro";
---

<section class="bg-gradient-to-t from-gray-50 to-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-8 sm:px-6 sm:py-24 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl text-center">
        Frequently Asked Questions
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-4 text-center text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide text-gray-600">
        Here are some common questions we get from our customers
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
          <button
            type="button"
            class="flex w-full items-center justify-between px-4 py-4 text-left"
          >
            <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">What is Astroship?</span>
            <span class="ml-6 flex items-center">
              <svg
                class="h-6 w-6 rotate-0 transform text-gray-400 transition-transform duration-200"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"
                />
              </svg>
            </span>
          </button>
          <div class="px-4 pb-4 pt-2">
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Astroship is a modern website template built with Astro framework, specifically designed for startups, SaaS products, and marketing websites. It offers elegant design and exceptional performance.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
          <button
            type="button"
            class="flex w-full items-center justify-between px-4 py-4 text-left"
          >
            <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">Do I need programming experience to use Astroship?</span>
            <span class="ml-6 flex items-center">
              <svg
                class="h-6 w-6 rotate-0 transform text-gray-400 transition-transform duration-200"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"
                />
              </svg>
            </span>
          </button>
          <div class="px-4 pb-4 pt-2">
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Not necessarily. Astroship provides clear documentation and simple configuration options that make it accessible even without extensive programming experience. However, if you do have programming skills, you can customize it even further.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
          <button
            type="button"
            class="flex w-full items-center justify-between px-4 py-4 text-left"
          >
            <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">Is Astroship responsive?</span>
            <span class="ml-6 flex items-center">
              <svg
                class="h-6 w-6 rotate-0 transform text-gray-400 transition-transform duration-200"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"
                />
              </svg>
            </span>
          </button>
          <div class="px-4 pb-4 pt-2">
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Yes, Astroship is fully responsive. The website automatically adapts to different screen sizes, including desktop, tablet, and mobile devices, ensuring a great user experience across all platforms.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
          <button
            type="button"
            class="flex w-full items-center justify-between px-4 py-4 text-left"
          >
            <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">How can I get technical support?</span>
            <span class="ml-6 flex items-center">
              <svg
                class="h-6 w-6 rotate-0 transform text-gray-400 transition-transform duration-200"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"
                />
              </svg>
            </span>
          </button>
          <div class="px-4 pb-4 pt-2">
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We offer multiple support channels, including comprehensive documentation, community forums, and a dedicated technical support team. You can reach out through any of these channels to get the help you need.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
          <button
            type="button"
            class="flex w-full items-center justify-between px-4 py-4 text-left"
          >
            <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">Can I build an e-commerce website with Astroship?</span>
            <span class="ml-6 flex items-center">
              <svg
                class="h-6 w-6 rotate-0 transform text-gray-400 transition-transform duration-200"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"
                />
              </svg>
            </span>
          </button>
          <div class="px-4 pb-4 pt-2">
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              While Astroship is primarily designed for marketing and SaaS websites, its flexible architecture allows for e-commerce integration. You can easily add payment processing, shopping cart functionality, and other e-commerce features.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    const buttons = document.querySelectorAll('button');
    buttons.forEach(button => {
      button.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const content = button.nextElementSibling;
        const icon = button.querySelector('svg');
        const isOpen = content.style.display === 'block';
        
        // Close all panels
        document.querySelectorAll('button + div').forEach(div => {
          div.style.display = 'none';
        });
        document.querySelectorAll('button svg').forEach(svg => {
          svg.style.transform = 'rotate(0deg)';
        });

        // Toggle clicked panel
        if (!isOpen) {
          content.style.display = 'block';
          icon.style.transform = 'rotate(180deg)';
        }
      });
    });

    // Hide all panels initially
    document.querySelectorAll('button + div').forEach(div => {
      div.style.display = 'none';
    });
  });
</script>

<style>
  button + div {
    transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
  }
  
  svg {
    transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
  }
</style>
